Ejercicio HTML Server Python module vs Apache Server

Python module advantages:
Fast.
Simple to setup.
Abstract (blackbox).
Less maintenance.

Python module disadvantages:
Fragile(not resilient).
Weak(for lite web services only, scarse resources available)
Less safe (Black box).

Apache Server advantages:
Robust/Resilient.
Resourceful (better services capability).
Modularized/Intuituve/Easy to understand.
More safe.

Apache Server disadvantages:
Long steps to setup.
More files to mantain.
Firewall rules intervene.
More maintenance.